msgid ""
"A variant of \"no-referrer-when-downgrade\", with the addition that "
"\"Referer\" is not sent if the parent request was using ``file://`` or "
"``s3://`` scheme."
msgstr ""
"\"no referrer-when en-downgrade\"的变体，如果父请求使用 ``file://`` 或 "
"``s3://`` 方案，则\"Referer\"不会被发送。"

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:397
msgid ""
"Scrapy's default referrer policy — just like `\"no-referrer-when-"
"downgrade\"`_, the W3C-recommended value for browsers — will send a non-"
"empty \"Referer\" header from any ``http(s)://`` to any ``https://`` URL, "
"even if the domain is different."
msgstr ""
"Scrapy 的默认引用策略——就像`no referrer-when en-downgrade`_'， 为浏览器推荐"
"的 W3C 值 — — 将从任何 ``http(s)://`` 中发送一个非空的 \"Referer\" 头到任何 "
"``https://`` URL，即使域是不同的。"

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:402
msgid ""
"`\"same-origin\"`_ may be a better choice if you want to remove referrer "
"information for cross-domain requests."
msgstr ""
"`\"相同的原始\"_可能是一个更好的选择，如果您想要移除跨域请求的推荐信息。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.NoReferrerPolicy:1
msgid "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-no-referrer"
msgstr "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-referrer"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.NoReferrerPolicy:3
msgid ""
"The simplest policy is \"no-referrer\", which specifies that no referrer "
"information is to be sent along with requests made from a particular request "
"client to any origin. The header will be omitted entirely."
msgstr ""
"最简单的政策是“不要提到”， 其中规定不应向任何来源发送推荐人的信息和特定请求客"
"户的请求。 标题将被完全省略。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.NoReferrerWhenDowngradePolicy:1
msgid ""
"https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-no-referrer-when-"
"downgrade"
msgstr ""
"https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-no-referrer-when en-"
"downgrade"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.NoReferrerWhenDowngradePolicy:3
msgid ""
"The \"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" policy sends a full URL along with "
"requests from a TLS-protected environment settings object to a potentially "
"trustworthy URL, and requests from clients which are not TLS-protected to "
"any origin."
msgstr ""
"\"不推荐的时候降级\"政策将一个完整的 URL 和来自一个 TLS 保护环境设置对象的请"
"求发送到一个可能值得信任的 URL。 和来自不受TLS-保护的客户端的请求。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.NoReferrerWhenDowngradePolicy:7
msgid ""
"Requests from TLS-protected clients to non-potentially trustworthy URLs, on "
"the other hand, will contain no referrer information. A Referer HTTP header "
"will not be sent."
msgstr ""
"另一方面，由 TLS 保护的客户端向不可信任的 URL 的请求将不包含参考信息。"
"Referer HTTP 头将不会发送。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.NoReferrerWhenDowngradePolicy:11
msgid ""
"This is a user agent's default behavior, if no policy is otherwise specified."
msgstr "这是用户代理的默认行为，如果没有指定其他策略。"

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:409
msgid ""
"\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" policy is the W3C-recommended default, and is "
"used by major web browsers."
msgstr "\"不推荐当降级时\"策略是 W3C 推荐的默认值，并被主要浏览器使用。"

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:412
msgid ""
"However, it is NOT Scrapy's default referrer policy (see :class:"
"`DefaultReferrerPolicy`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.SameOriginPolicy:1
msgid "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-same-origin"
msgstr "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-some-original"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.SameOriginPolicy:3
msgid ""
"The \"same-origin\" policy specifies that a full URL, stripped for use as a "
"referrer, is sent as referrer information when making same-origin requests "
"from a particular request client."
msgstr ""
"“相同来源”策略规定了一个完整的 URL，用作推荐器， 当从特定请求客户端提出相同来"
"源请求时，将作为推荐信息发送。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.SameOriginPolicy:6
msgid ""
"Cross-origin requests, on the other hand, will contain no referrer "
"information. A Referer HTTP header will not be sent."
msgstr "另一方面，跨源请求将不包含引用信息。Referer HTTP 标头将不会发送。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.OriginPolicy:1
msgid "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-origin"
msgstr ""
"https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-origin-policy-original"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.OriginPolicy:3
msgid ""
"The \"origin\" policy specifies that only the ASCII serialization of the "
"origin of the request client is sent as referrer information when making "
"both same-origin requests and cross-origin requests from a particular "
"request client."
msgstr ""
"“原始”政策规定，在提出相同原始请求和来自特定请求客户的跨原始请求时，只将请求"
"客户端的 ASCII 序列化作为参考信息发送。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.StrictOriginPolicy:1
msgid "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-strict-origin"
msgstr "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-strict-original"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.StrictOriginPolicy:3
msgid ""
"The \"strict-origin\" policy sends the ASCII serialization of the origin of "
"the request client when making requests: - from a TLS-protected environment "
"settings object to a potentially trustworthy URL, and - from non-TLS-"
"protected environment settings objects to any origin."
msgstr ""
"“严格起源”政策在请求时发送请求客户端来源的ASCII序列化：- 从 TLS 受保护的环境"
"设置对象到一个可能值得信任的 URL， - 从不受TLS-保护的环境设置对象到任何源."

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.StrictOriginPolicy:8
msgid ""
"Requests from TLS-protected request clients to non- potentially trustworthy "
"URLs, on the other hand, will contain no referrer information. A Referer "
"HTTP header will not be sent."
msgstr ""
"另一方面，来自 TLS 保护的请求客户端对不可信的 URL 的请求将不包含参考信息。 "
"Referer HTTP 头将不会发送。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.OriginWhenCrossOriginPolicy:1
msgid ""
"https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-origin-when-cross-"
"origin"
msgstr ""
"https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-policy-origin-when-"
"cross-origin-"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.OriginWhenCrossOriginPolicy:3
msgid ""
"The \"origin-when-cross-origin\" policy specifies that a full URL, stripped "
"for use as a referrer, is sent as referrer information when making same-"
"origin requests from a particular request client, and only the ASCII "
"serialization of the origin of the request client is sent as referrer "
"information when making cross-origin requests from a particular request "
"client."
msgstr ""
"“原始跨源”政策规定，完整的 URL，可作为推荐人使用， 当从特定请求客户端提出相同"
"来源请求时，作为推荐信息发送， 并且只有ASCII序列化请求客户端的来源，在从特定"
"请求客户端提出交叉请求时作为参考信息发送。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.StrictOriginWhenCrossOriginPolicy:1
msgid ""
"https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-strict-origin-when-"
"cross-origin"
msgstr ""
"https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-strict-origin-when-"
"cross-origin-"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.StrictOriginWhenCrossOriginPolicy:3
msgid ""
"The \"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" policy specifies that a full URL, "
"stripped for use as a referrer, is sent as referrer information when making "
"same-origin requests from a particular request client, and only the ASCII "
"serialization of the origin of the request client when making cross-origin "
"requests:"
msgstr ""
"“严格源头跨源”政策规定，完整的 URL，可作为推荐人使用， 当从特定请求客户端提出"
"相同来源请求时，作为推荐信息发送， 并且只有ASCII在提出跨源请求时将请求客户端"
"的来源序列化："

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.StrictOriginWhenCrossOriginPolicy:9
msgid ""
"from a TLS-protected environment settings object to a potentially "
"trustworthy URL, and"
msgstr "从 TLS 受保护的环境设置对象到一个可能值得信任的 URL，和"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.StrictOriginWhenCrossOriginPolicy:10
msgid "from non-TLS-protected environment settings objects to any origin."
msgstr "从非 TLS 保护的环境设置对象到任何来源。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.StrictOriginWhenCrossOriginPolicy:12
msgid ""
"Requests from TLS-protected clients to non- potentially trustworthy URLs, on "
"the other hand, will contain no referrer information. A Referer HTTP header "
"will not be sent."
msgstr ""
"另一方面，受TLS保护的客户端对不可信的 URL 的请求将不包含参考信息。 Referer "
"HTTP 头将不会发送。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.UnsafeUrlPolicy:1
msgid "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-unsafe-url"
msgstr "https://www.w3.org/TR/referrer-policy/#referrer-policy-unsafe-url"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.UnsafeUrlPolicy:3
msgid ""
"The \"unsafe-url\" policy specifies that a full URL, stripped for use as a "
"referrer, is sent along with both cross-origin requests and same-origin "
"requests made from a particular request client."
msgstr ""
"“不安全-url”策略规定，一个完整的 URL，可作为推荐人使用。 与不同来源的请求和来"
"自特定请求客户的相同请求一起发送。"

#: ../../../../scrapy/spidermiddlewares/referer.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.spidermiddlewares.referer.UnsafeUrlPolicy:7
msgid ""
"Note: The policy's name doesn't lie; it is unsafe. This policy will leak "
"origins and paths from TLS-protected resources to insecure origins. "
"Carefully consider the impact of setting such a policy for potentially "
"sensitive documents."
msgstr ""
"注意：该策略的名称不会是假的；它是不安全的。该策略将泄露来源和路径，从受TLS-"
"保护的资源到不安全的来源。 认真考虑为潜在敏感文件制定这样一项政策所产生的影"
"响。"

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:426
msgid "\"unsafe-url\" policy is NOT recommended."
msgstr "不推荐“不安全-url”政策。"

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:440
msgid "UrlLengthMiddleware"
msgstr "UrlLengthMiddleware"

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:447
msgid "Filters out requests with URLs longer than URLLENGTH_LIMIT"
msgstr "过滤带有URL长于URLLENGTH_LIMIT"

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:449
msgid ""
"The :class:`UrlLengthMiddleware` can be configured through the following "
"settings (see the settings documentation for more info):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/spider-middleware.rst:452
msgid ""
":setting:`URLLENGTH_LIMIT` - The maximum URL length to allow for crawled "
"URLs."
msgstr ""
